casebody.data:
STATE EX REL. WYLIE-BROWN
v.
O'LEARY. 2018-0016 Supreme Court of Ohio. April 25, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Prohibition. On respondents' motions to dismiss. Motions granted. Cause dismissed. On relator's motion for default judgment and motion for declaratory judgment and/or demand for contempt order. Motions denied as moot.
